   "source": [
    "n = 5\n",
    "t = range(-1,stop=1,length=n+1)\n",
    "y = @. t^2 + t + 0.05*sin(20*t)\n",
    "\n",
    "using Plots\n",
    "scatter(t,y,label=\"data\",leg=:top)"
   ]

    "n = 18\n",
    "t = range(-1,stop=1,length=n+1)\n",
    "y = @. t^2 + t + 0.05*sin(20*t)\n",
    "\n",
    "plot(t,y,m=:o,l=nothing,label=\"data\",leg=:top)"
   ]
